name: Gateway City Shopping Centre
directions: Available during Centre opening hours.   Near the food court.
comment: Wow.  Gender neutral Wheelchair accessible single occupant stall; has lowered toilet with grabrails, lowered basin and change table, nappy and sanitary disposal.   Signs in braille,  electric door and lock,  assistance button.   Separate gender neutral parenting room.  It has four lockable feeding rooms.  Two include toilets, all have a chair, room for prams and other children,  change table, rubbish bin and assistance button.  All doors and locks are manual.   Main room has chairs,  multiple change areas,  fully plumbed baby bath, separate handwashing basin, rubbish and nappy disposal, power points, and microwave.   Near the main  (gendered) toilets is a rest area with comfy chairs.

Long term paid parking available at the bottom of the stairs, includes designated disabled parking.   No designated change tables, but low benches which could be used.   Signs include braille.   The surface around the block is very uneven.
